{
  "type": "Collection",
  "id": "earthcare-marine-stratocumulus-transitions",
  "stac_version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The EarthCARE Marine Stratocumulus Organization and Transition Dataset includes related data products and model artifacts describing mesoscale cloud structure, microphysics, precipitation, and cloud evolution: (1) manually labelled EarthCARE/MSI and GOES/ABI image datasets for cloud-structure classification, (2) fine-tuned CNN model weights for MSI and GOES classification, (3) an EarthCARE stratocumulus scene catalogue linking cloud organization with active/passive microphysical and precipitation retrievals, and (4) GOES and ERA5-trajectory-based datasets identifying and characterizing closed-to-open-cell transitions.",
